      <p>
A subtype of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
      </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_activity">CARE ACTIVITY</xref>
 is the provision of an individual instance of care to a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 given by one or more 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONALS</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
Subtypes of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_activity">CARE ACTIVITY</xref>
 are:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_contact">CARE CONTACT</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_clinical_intervention">CLINICAL INTERVENTION</xref>
               <p>.</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_activity">CARE ACTIVITIES</xref>
 include:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_multidisciplinary_team_meeting">Multidisciplinary Team Meeting</xref>
         </li>
      </ul>
